sys_properties.description: The free version of API NBA only allows for 10 calls per minute. This property, if set to true, will add a delay between calls so that more than 10 calls will never be made in a minute. Note that this will make many calls take 5+ minutes, and should only be used if you are using the free version of API NBA.
sys_properties.name: x_0294_nba.sleep
